sql:
SELECT report_name
FROM financial_reports
ORDER BY report_name ASC;

external_knowledge:
* The fiscal year is a 12-month period used for financial reporting and budgeting; 
* The net income is the total earnings of a company after deducting all expenses and taxes; 
* Depreciation is the decrease in value of an asset over its useful life; 
* Non-cash items are income or expenses that are not exchanged for cash.

